                            <author>Kātyāyana</author>
                            <incipit><locus>F.4 </locus>pūrvottaradakṣiṇaśadvānāṃ deśavācaka tha [ta
                                in margin] yā ̐bhidhānaṃ nātaḥ strīliṃgāpekṣā
                                maṃdalasyāvadhitvaprakaraṇāt || iti grahādisthāpanaṃ...</incipit>
                            <explicit><locus>F.14v </locus>...viprān [na]maskṛtya visarjayet iti
                                gṛhaśāti kātyāyanakṛtā samāptā subhaṃ oṃ yajñopavītaṃ paramaṃ
                                pavitraṃ prajāpater yat sahajaṃ purastāt āyuḥ samagraṃ pratimuṃca
                                śubhraṃ yajñopavītaṃ balam ast[u] tejāḥ 1 grahāṇāṃ śāṃti likhitā
                                saṃpūrṇaṃ saṃvat 1927 māse vaiśākhe āravāsaraikādaśyāṃ samāptam
                                ||</explicit>
                            <filiation><note>The final verse in the explicit beginning yajñopavītaṃ
                                    is the last verse in the
                                <title>Yajñopavītamantra</title></note>.Cf.
                                    <idno><!--<ref target="ADD URL">B.20.kk</ref>--></idno>
                            </filiation>
                        </msItem>

